www.merseyrail.org
4
cf_clearance
This Cloudflare cookie is used to maximize network resources, manage traffic and protect the website from malicious traffic. Clearance cookies store proof of security challenge passed.
Fuelius.Clients.Merseyrail.DestinationPlanner.PlannerSessionKey
This cookie stores the users unique Id for the Destination Merseyside planner.
station_destination
This cookie is used to store the destination station that visitors select when journey planning. This information is then used when the user loads the journey planner any other subsequent times.
station_origin
This cookie is used to store the origin station that visitors select when journey planning. This information is then used when the user loads the journey planner at any other subsequent times.
Preference cookies enable a website to remember information that changes the way the website behaves or looks, like your preferred language or the region that you are in.
We do not use cookies of this type.
Statistic cookies help website owners to understand how visitors interact with websites by collecting and reporting information anonymously.
